<inglise>(1) Upon non-performance of obligations provided for in &sect;&sect; 170-175 or subsections 176 (1) and (3) of this Act, a public servant shall be released from the service pursuant to this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Teenistuja vabastatakse teenistusest k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi 1. l&otilde;ike alusel vabastamise vormistamise dokumendis m&auml;rgitud p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A public servant shall be released from the service pursuant to subsection (1) of this section as of the date specified in the document of release. </inglise>
