<eesti>(1) Isikule, kes k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel on teenistuses, arvutatakse teenistusstaa&zcaron;i &sect;-des 153-156 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The length of service of a person who is in the service upon the entry into force of this Act shall be calculated pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect;&sect; 153-156. </inglise>
<eesti>Paragrahvi 153 punktis 1 s&auml;testatud tegevuse hulka arvatakse enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist riigi v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse ametiasutustes t&ouml;&ouml;tatud aeg ja nimetatud asutustele allunud ettev&otilde;tetes, asutustes ja organisatsioonides ametikohtadel, mis eeldasid avaliku v&otilde;imu &uuml;lesannete t&auml;itmist, t&ouml;&ouml;tatud aeg, v&auml;lja arvatud teenistusaeg endise NSV Liidu julgeolekuorganites v&otilde;i relvaj&otilde;ududes. </eesti>
<inglise>The activities provided for in clause 153 1) shall include the period of employment in state or local government administrative agencies and the period of employment in positions which required the performance of duties related to exercise of public authority in the enterprises, agencies and organisations which are/were subordinate to the specified administrative agencies before entry into force of this Act, except the period of service in security organisations and armed forces of the former USSR. </inglise>
